{"tid":1612083,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實陳同佳岀獄點解要召喚神獸","createTime":"2019-10-02T06:47:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T06:55:26.000Z","uid":311321,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2bed4ef7f0aa73fa55e5f91bbb6a8930417087e0","tid":1612083,"uid":311321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:47:34.000Z","msg":"其實搞到今時今日滿城風雨嘅真係關陳同佳事咩？陳同佳只係個導火線，令到林奠有籍口去修訂條例，假設冇左陳同佳嘅岀現，唔通林奠就會乖乖地乜都唔做過幾年退休？<strong>絕對唔會</strong> ，佢只會繼續揾機會去賣港，討好阿爺。無可否認今次陳同佳係今場運動嘅起因，但係亦都係今次嘅運動令到香港人團結起嚟，亦都發現到好多社會上嘅問題 (警犬濫捕、警權大過天)，所以我地更加應該珍惜今次嘅機會，去保護屬於我地嘅香港！至於陳同佳就由得佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好令運動嘅焦點變得分散，緊記我地要對準政權。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecfef1b2d50313dd54499811f9bbf4ebab09c043","tid":1612083,"uid":311321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:48:46.000Z","msg":"<strong>推</strong>"},{"pid":"505ae4785de885eecac7372d69f2b9edc855c4ef","tid":1612083,"uid":147496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"推佢上前線"},{"pid":"227380a6a48fe2257208d3c8016c280c2d59d2eb","tid":1612083,"uid":311321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"505ae4785de885eecac7372d69f2b9edc855c4ef","tid":1612083,"uid":147496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"推佢上前線"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"FF緊佢係深黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe854f4260e0066ffb944ab32147f853babb50e0","tid":1612083,"uid":147496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"227380a6a48fe2257208d3c8016c280c2d59d2eb","tid":1612083,"uid":311321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"505ae4785de885eecac7372d69f2b9edc855c4ef","tid":1612083,"uid":147496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"推佢上前線"},"c